title: The Giants Traded OBJ?! And More Transaction Reactions | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
The Giants shipped Odell Beckham Jr. to the Browns, the Jets signed Le’Veon Bell, the Raiders dealt for Antonio Brown, the Ravens landed Earl Thomas, and more roster news from around the league.

Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
